e fork outer tube.","Before tightening, cover the top cap with a suitable masking tape to protect its anodized finish from tool damage.","Tighten the top cap to ","35 Nm",".","It is much easier to tighten the top cap when the fork has been refitted.","Refit the fork assembly (see ","Front Fork - Installation",")."],"viewCount":0,"infoType":"InfoType09","createdAt":"2024-04-16T10:55:45.803Z","updatedAt":"2024-04-16T10:55:45.803Z","__v":0}